Our passion for sneakers, streetwear, and technology inspired us to create a globally recognized Web3 brand that bridges the gap between the physical world and the Metaverse. The new era of flex is here.

The Hype Section is owned by Carlos Gil and Reggie Williams, successful entrepreneurs with significant experience in brand and community building, including marketing, e-commerce, professional sports, and entertainment backgrounds.

Our passion for sneakers, streetwear, and technology inspired us to create a globally recognized Web3 brand that bridges the gap between the physical world and the Metaverse. assets.name: #1075 Three Dee
assets.description:
Rxnegade RX Apes are a collection of NFTs where the images are selected and customised by owners using a unique image generator.

Each RX Ape is part of a sub-collection linked to a Rxnegades member. Each member provides their own unique utility and receives royalties for secondary sales of RX Apes linked to them using a unique on-chain relationship.

Visit the website for more information about the project and the utility associated with this ape.

asset_contract.name: Rxnegade RX Apes
asset_contract.description:
MINTING LIVE at https://projectrxnegade.com

"The most fun and addictive minting experience." - Every RX Ape minter, 2022.

The first Project Rxnegade collection. 19,946 Ape NFTs generated randomly, on-demand, in real-time at the point of minting by Rxnegades members. Don't like your ape? Yeet it and get a new image, once per day, per token, until you are happy, then name it. You don't wait for the reveal, the reveal waits for you. 

Each RX Ape token is forever linked to the original Rxnegades member that minted it - using the new NFT Royalty Standard, the member that minted the RX Ape token receives royalties (0-10%) on all secondary sales (on marketplaces that support the standard).
